message:
Hello Friends!

If you're looking for something AWESOME to do next weekend, check out Agape Dance Collective's first show! We are striving to minister to the arts community, and we have created a show with a vision to tackle important and tough questions about God and our humanity through movement. Ministry in the arts community is TOUGH, and we'd love to have your support. Plus, there are some absolutely beautiful movers in this show.

Check out our Facebook page (you can find all the event details under the "events" tab): https://www.facebook.com/agapedancecollective/?fref=ts

and here is our kickstarter campaign, we have a video and tons of other info: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1869710723/agape-dance-collective/description

Thanks guys!
